str:Codelist.com:Name: Country
str:Codelist.com:Description: This code list provides information on the reporting entities for which statistical data is collected and reported: geographical entities (countries and other territories), economic entities, and country groups (aggregates or collective categories for which statistics are calculated).

str:ConceptScheme.com:Name: Master System Concepts
str:ConceptScheme.com:Description: The Master System Concept Scheme contain system concepts and related definitions that are required for certain functionality.

str:Concept.com:Name: Frequency
str:Concept.com:Description: Time interval at which observations occur over a given time period.

str:Concept.com:Name: Scale
str:Concept.com:Description: Exponent in base 10 specified so that multiplying the observation numeric values by 10^UNIT_MULT gives a value expressed in the unit of measure.

str:Concept.com:Name: Precision
str:Concept.com:Description: Accuracy of the measurement.

str:Concept.com:Name: Decimals Displayed
str:Concept.com:Description: Number of digits of an observation to the right of a decimal point used for display in the system.

str:Concept.com:Name: Observation value
str:Concept.com:Description: Value of a particular variable.

str:Concept.com:Name: Time Period
str:Concept.com:Description: Timespan or point in time to which the observation actually refers.

str:Concept.com:Name: ID
str:Concept.com:Description: A user-friendly string strictly bound to predefined valueset used to identify the resource.

str:Concept.com:Name: DOI
str:Concept.com:Description: DOI (Digital Object Identifier) is a public identifier for selected resources published on the data portal. Users use it for citing the resource.

str:Concept.com:Name: ISBN
str:Concept.com:Description: An 8-digit numeric code, which identifies the printed or electronic edition of a periodical.

str:Concept.com:Name: Dataset
str:Concept.com:Description: A related dataset in which the described data is included.

str:Concept.com:Name: Name
str:Concept.com:Description: A name given to the resource. This is a text string assigned by the dataset owner without any authoritative guidelines.

str:Concept.com:Name: Content Type
str:Concept.com:Description: The nature or type of the resource.

str:Concept.com:Name: Department
str:Concept.com:Description: The responsible department / division ultimately accountable for the resource created by or to the organization (e.g. IMF)

str:Concept.com:Name: Author
str:Concept.com:Description: The person or organization responsible for resource’s substantive and intellectual content.

str:Concept.com:Name: Unit of Measure
str:Concept.com:Description: A unit of measurement of the observations in the indicator (e.g. Euro, square kilometre, percentage).

str:Concept.com:Name: Reference Period
str:Concept.com:Description: Indicates the time period for which the data is based on. This is for real or index series and it is synonymous with base period.

str:Concept.com:Name: Frequency
str:Concept.com:Description: The frequency of the timeseries (e.g. monthly, quarterly, yearly).

str:Concept.com:Name: Country
str:Concept.com:Description: Country or specific areas for which statistics are provided or is covered by the resource.

str:Concept.com:Name: Counterpart Country
str:Concept.com:Description: Country or specific areas within which the reference area or reporter had the transaction with.

str:Concept.com:Name: Geographical Region
str:Concept.com:Description: The geographical area or location that relates or is covered by the resource (UNSD / M49 Geograpical Regions).

str:Concept.com:Name: Time Period
str:Concept.com:Description: An interval of time that is named or defined by its start and end dates of the data in a resource.

str:Concept.com:Name: Publication Date
str:Concept.com:Description: The date of formal issuance (e.g., publication) of the resource.

str:Concept.com:Name: Updated Date
str:Concept.com:Description: Most recent date on which the resource was changed, updated or modified.

str:Concept.com:Name: Revision Type
str:Concept.com:Description: A revision is defined as the numerical difference between two vintages of the same data point.

str:Concept.com:Name: Full Description
str:Concept.com:Description: Textual long description of the resource.

str:Concept.com:Name: Dataset Topic
str:Concept.com:Description: A topic of the resource.

str:Concept.com:Name: Keywords - DO NOT USE
str:Concept.com:Description: The subject of the resource that is represented using keywords.

str:Concept.com:Name: Language
str:Concept.com:Description: The primary language of the resource.

str:Concept.com:Name: Metadata Notes
str:Concept.com:Description: A statement providing explanatory information about data.

str:Concept.com:Name: Methodology
str:Concept.com:Description: Reference to the conceptual statistical framework and underlying statistical methodology used for the dataset (e.g. country specific).

str:Concept.com:Name: Release Notes
str:Concept.com:Description: It contains a description of the differences between this release and a previous release of the dataset.

str:Concept.com:Name: Short Source Citation
str:Concept.com:Description: The short source citation of the resource following IMF style guide recommendations.

str:Concept.com:Name: Full Source Citation
str:Concept.com:Description: The attribution of the resource.

str:Concept.com:Name: Security Classification
str:Concept.com:Description: Classification of the resource based on who can access it, what is its security status, how sensitive is its information and what are its distribution rights.

str:Concept.com:Name: License
str:Concept.com:Description: Information on the licence for distribution of the resource, under which the resource is made available.

str:Concept.com:Name: Suggested Citation
str:Concept.com:Description: Citation of the resource by referencing the resource in a bibliographic format, acknowledging the resource as a first class output.

str:Concept.com:Name: Contact Point
str:Concept.com:Description: Point of contact for the dataset.

str:Concept.com:Name: Format
str:Concept.com:Description: Format version of the desscribed resource.

str:Concept.com:Name: Observation Status
str:Concept.com:Description: Coded information about the "status" of an observation.

str:Concept.com:Name: Indicator Topic
str:Concept.com:Description: Topic of an indicator

str:Concept.com:Name: Dataset Display Name
str:Concept.com:Description: Display name of a dataset

str:Concept.com:Name: Dataset Methodology Notes
str:Concept.com:Description: Notes on methodology

str:Concept.com:Name: Indicator Methodology Notes
str:Concept.com:Description: Notes on methodology

str:Concept.com:Name: Dataset Comment
str:Concept.com:Description: Commentary on a dataset

str:Concept.com:Name: Sharing Status
str:Concept.com:Description: Communicates data sharing permission where the originator labeling information to indicate what further dissemination, if any, can be undertaken by the recipient.

str:Concept.com:Name: Dataset Keywords
str:Concept.com:Description: The subject of the resource that is represented using keywords (dataset level).

str:Concept.com:Name: Indicator Keywords
str:Concept.com:Description: The subject of the resource that is represented using keywords (indicator level).

str:Concept.com:Name: Publisher
str:Concept.com:Description: An entity responsible for making the resource available.
